{"article_id":"99vMS9EymAp6egLG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump said","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"he 's not concerned by North Korea 's recent missile tests","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"and endorsed Kim Jong Un 's attack on fellow American and former Vice President Joe Biden in a press conference in Tokyo Monday .","depth":2},{"id":3,"text":"Interested in Donald Trump ?","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Add Donald Trump as an interest","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"to stay up to date on the latest Donald Trump news , video , and analysis from .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Add Interest","depth":3},{"id":7,"text":"`` Kim Jong-Un made a statement","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that Joe Biden is a low IQ individual .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"He probably is based on his record .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"I think","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"I agree with him on that , ''","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Trump said .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Trump was asked","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"if he is siding with a dictator over a fellow citizen and former U.S. vice president .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Trump responded","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"that he does n't take sides","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"and , on foreign soil , went on to call the Obama administration a `` disaster . '' `` I can tell you","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"that Joe Biden was a disaster ,","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"his administration with President Obama , they were basically a disaster","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"when it came to so many things , ''","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"the president said .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"`` Whether it was economy ,","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"whether it was military , defense ,","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"no matter what it was .","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"They had a lot of problems .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"So I 'm not a fan . ''","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Despite Trump and Abe saying","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"that they are on the same page","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"when it comes to North Korea ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Trump has downplayed the North 's recent missile tests","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"-- drawing a sharp contrast to the assessment of his own national security adviser and his Japanese host .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"North Korea fired off some small weapons ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"which disturbed some of my people , and others , but not me .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"I have confidence","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"that Chairman Kim will keep his promise to me ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"& also smiled","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"when he called Swampman Joe Biden a low IQ individual , & worse .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Perhaps that 's sending me a signal ?","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"May 26 , 2019","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"`` My people think","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"it could have been a violation ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"as you know , ''","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"the president said .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"`` I view it differently .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"I view it as a man ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"perhaps he wants to get attention ,","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"and perhaps not .","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"Who knows ?","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"It does n't matter .","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"All","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"I know","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"is that there have been no nuclear tests .","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"There have been no ballistic missiles going out .","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"There have been no long-range missiles going out .","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"And I think","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"that someday we 'll have a deal . ''","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"Yet the president 's national security adviser John Bolton said","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"that the recent missile tests are `` no doubt '' violations of U.N. Security Council resolutions .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Trump said","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"he is in `` no rush '' for North Korea to denuclearize .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"`` I am very happy with the way","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"it 's going .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"And intelligent people agree , ''","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"he added ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"praising Kim as a `` smart man . ''","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"The president will be back in Japan at the end of next month for the G-20 summit","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"as a trade war with China looms .","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"Though Trump said in the press conference Monday","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"that the U.S. is not ready to make a trade deal with China ,","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"the president 's economic adviser said earlier this month","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"that there is a `` strong possibility '' of a meeting between Trump and Chinese leader , Xi Jinping , at the meeting .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":147,"left":76,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":75,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":75,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":79,"right":145,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":79,"left":78,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":3,"right":77,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":77,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":139,"right":144,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":139,"left":98,"right":138,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":84,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":83,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":81,"right":82,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"}